snippet.title: Sticky Pigeons (Game Jam) Gameplay
snippet.description:
Sticky Pigeons is a 2D 2-player versus game made during a game jam in Beirut Lebanon.

Download: https://groovyantoid.itch.io/sticky-pigeons
